  "subject": "[SO] Fix so-openstack-adapter support for Keystone V3 api",
  "commit_message": "[SO] Fix so-openstack-adapter support for Keystone V3 api\n\nCurrently so-openstack-adapter configuration file contains hardcoded v2.0\nKeystone endpoint. This fix allows for defining Keystone api version via\nvalues/override file.\n\nChange-Id: Ib81c2888784d3d41c1ac2464c122a426743023dd\nIssue-ID: OOM-2866\nSigned-off-by: Marcin Wilk <m.wilk@samsung.com>\n(cherry picked from commit ad9b376c2c47e46e30590bb0a8fe66fdb7badbab)\n",
